text: Yves Vandewalle (born June 5, 1950 in Freiburg im Breisgau) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Yvelines department,http://www.assemblee-nationale.fr/13/tribun/fiches_id/267606.asp and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:People from Freiburg im Breisgau Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Yves Vandewalle
